This document is to provide a detailed understanding on the tables and the corresponding columns.
  There are three tables for use and they are
    1. gold.dim_customers
    2.gold.dim_products
    3.gold.fact_sales


1. gold.dim_customers

* Purpose: This table stores the details of customers.
*Columns:

|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|Column Name      |  Data Type      |  Description                                                    |
|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
|customer_key     |      INT        | Surrogate Key uniquely identifies every record in the table     |
|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------| 
|customer_id      |      INT        | Unique numerical identifier assigned to each customer           |
|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|  
|customer_number  |NVARCHAR(50)     | Alphanumeric identifier for tracking  and referencing           |
|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|     
|first_name       |NVARCHAR(50)     | Customer's first name                                           |
|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|     
|last_name        |NVARCHAR(50)     | Customer's last name                                            |  
|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|           
|country          |NVARCHAR(50)     |Customer's country of residence                                  |                  
|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
|marital_status   |NVARCHAR(50)     | Customer's marital status                                       |
|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
|gender           |NVARCHAR(50)     | Customer's gender                                               |
|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
|birthdate        |DATE             | Customer's birthdate in 'YYYY-MM-DD' format                     |
|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
|create_date      |DATE             | Date on which the customer's record created in the system       |
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------




2. gold.dim_products

* Purpose: This table stores the details of products.
*Columns:

|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|Column Name      |  Data Type      |  Description                                                    |
|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
|product_key      |INT        | Surrogate Key uniquely identifies every record in the table           |
|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------| 
|product_id       |INT        | Unique numerical identifier assigned to each customer                 |
|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|  
|product_number   |NVARCHAR(50)     | Alphanumeric identifier for tracking  and referencing           |
|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|     
|product_name     |NVARCHAR(50)     | Product Name                                                    |
|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|     
|category_id      |NVARCHAR(50)     |Product category ID                                              |  
|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|           
|category         |NVARCHAR(50)     |Products category name                                           |                  
|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
|subcategory      |NVARCHAR(50)     |Products subcategory name                                        |
|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
|maintenance      |NVARCHAR(50)     | whether product requires time to time maintenance or not        |
|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
|cost             |DATE             | cost of the product                                             |
|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
|product_line     |DATE             | the product belongs to which series( eg road, mountain..        |
|-----------------|-----------------|-----------------------------------------------------------------|
|start_date       |DATE             | Date on which the product's record created in the system        |
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


3. gold.fact_sales

* Purpose: This table stores the fact details of sales.
*Columns:

|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|Column Name      |  Data Type      |  Description                                                    |
|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
|order_number     |VARCHAR(50)      | Surrogate Key uniquely identifies every record in the table     |
|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------| 
|product_key      |INT              | Surrogate key linking the product table                         |
|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|  
|customer_key     |INT              | Surrogate key linking the customer table            |           |
|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|     
|order_date       |DATE             | Date on which order is placed ('YYYY-MM'DD')                    |
|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|     
|ship_date        |DATE             | Date on which order is shipped ('YYYY-MM'DD')                   |  
|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|           
|due_date         |DATE             |Date on which order is due ('YYYY-MM'DD')                        |                  
|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
|sales_amount     |INT              | Total amount of sales of the line item                          |
|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
|quantity         |INT              | Total quantity of the line items                                |
|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
|price            |INT              |Price of individual items                                        |
|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
